description: WHAT WE DO?Bring you Fresh salads and wraps fast. Our rapid fire line sends out food at an alarming rate. Be on your toes because we move fast. Our goal is to get you back to your life with some first rate fuel. Simply the best salads on earth. Period.WHAT WE ARE MADE OF?Premium, organic, natural, and most importantly FRESH ingredients. The lettuce on your salad or wrap walked into our doors this morning. The chicken was marinated for 24 hours and cooked on our ripping hot grill. The dressings are all hand made and chef designed to give you the best flavor for least amount of calories. We are made of the things that most food chains would never think of using. We only put what's best for us into us and we want you to too.
name: Fresh Junkie
